{"word":"Mule","slug":"mule","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Mule</b> Uses of:<br/> - For royal riders<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=29'>2Sa 13:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=9'>2Sa 18:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=33'>1Ki 1:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=38'>1Ki 1:38</a> <br/> - Ridden by posts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=8&verse=10'>Est 8:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=8&verse=14'>Est 8:14</a> <br/> - Ridden by saints in Isaiah's prophetic vision of the kingdom of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=66&verse=20'>Isa 66:20</a> <br/> - As pack animals<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=17'>2Ki 5:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=40'>1Ch 12:40</a> <br/> Tribute paid in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=25'>1Ki 10:25</a><br/> Used in barter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=14'>Eze 27:14</a><br/> Used by the captivity in returning from Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=66'>Ezr 2:66</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=68'>Neh 7:68</a><br/> Used in war<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=14&verse=15'>Zec 14:15</a>"}]}